<A>__{kelly hits the fresh air, looking around wildly. he runs for the edge of a cliff high over the ocean. he raises his hands, we see his palms are covered with those wicked spines and they are dripping a venomous fluid not too different in color from the wound on blobis face. but then suddenly, something is wrong. kelly buckles, clutching his stomach again. he squelches what would have been a scream of agony. he looks at his palms and the spikes are gone. kelly hears footsteps. suddenly out of the darkness sabretooth barrels toward him. kelly turns and leaps. sabretooth comes to the edge of the cliff. when he looks over, kellyis body has vanished. swallowed by the sea. only his clothes remain on the rocks below.}
